subsubsections.text_content:
This solution provides a framework where the home network can trigger a primary authentication due to various scenarios, i.e.
-	SOR/UPU Counter wraparound;
-	EPC to 5G interworking where KAUSF would not be available at UE and AUSF. And due to this, a few services will not work;
-	Any other scenarios where any authorized NF can invoke the primary reauthorization.
The solution provides an advanced detection solution where the SoR/UPU wraparound situation is detected in advance, i.e., the AUSF detects that the UPU/SoR counter will reach its max value in the next SoR/UPU case and takes precautionary measures in advance.
